{{nihongo|'''Kamohara Shrine'''|賀茂波爾神社}} is a [[shinto shrine]] in the [[Engishiki Jinmyōchō]]. It is located in [[Yamashiro Province]].<ref name=":0" /> It is a candidate shrine (ronsha) for {{ill|Q135038775|ltq=Q135038775|qid=Q135038775|1=Kamonohanino Shrine}}.<ref name=":0" /> With the alternative candidate being {{ill|Hajio Shrine (Otagi district)|lt=Hajio Shrine (Otagi district)|qid=Q135068695|1=Hajio Shrine (Otagi district)}}.<ref name=":0" />

It is a subshrine of {{ill|Shimogamo Shrine|lt=Shimogamo Shrine|ca|Santuari de Shimogamo|en|Shimogamo Shrine|eo|Sanktejo Ŝimogamo|es|Santuario Shimogamo|eu|Shimogamo santutegia|fa|معبد شیموگامو|fi|Shimogamo-jinja|fr|Shimogamo-jinja (Kyoto)|id|Kuil Shimogamo|ja|賀茂御祖神社|ko|가모미오야 신사|la|Templum Simogamo|my|ရှိမိုဂမိုနတ်ကျောင်း|pl|Shimogamo-jinja|pt|Kamomioya-jinja|ru|Симогамо-дзиндзя|simple|Shimogamo Shrine|sl|Svetišče Šimogamo|th|ศาลเจ้าชิโมงาโมะ|tr|Shimogamo Tapınağı|zh|賀茂御祖神社|qid=Q701620|1=Shimogamo Shrine}} and it has its own subshrine, an Inari Shrine. There is little more information available on it. 

